Dion Wired is opening a store in Centurion Mall, taking place on 25 October 2018. For the grand opening of their store, Dion Wired will hold a sale with specials on many of their products. The sale will go on from 25 to 28 October 2018, and the doors are set to open at 07:00 from tomorrow. Some of the great products on sale are shown below. It must be noted that there are stock limits on certain products advertised.       